# Admin Backend Standards

Trước khi code hoặc review bất kỳ thứ gì liên quan **Admin Service**, bắt buộc tuân thủ chuẩn backend chung (`.cursor/rules/social/social-backend-standards.mdc`) **và** toàn bộ quy tắc dưới đây. Source-of-truth nghiệp vụ: `docs/business-spec/admin-service-spec.md`.

## 1. Service Boundary

- **Own:** system configs + history, system announcements, admin action logs, user enforcements + logs, content moderation logs, `outbox_events`.
- **PostgreSQL only** cho MVP (`admin_db`, port local **5436**). Không MongoDB trong admin-service.
- **Không** truy cập DB Auth/Commerce/Social/Notification. Chỉ lưu `user_id` / `admin_id` (UUID logical reference). Profile/session/role/permission source-of-truth: **Auth Service**.
- **Không** lưu password, refresh token, admin session, OAuth credential trong Admin DB.
- Product/shop/review/order/post/comment state: **owner service** apply; Admin ghi quyết định + audit + publish event / gọi internal API khi cần đồng bộ.

## 2. Architecture & Package

Dependency flow: `delivery → application → domain → infrastructure` (không đảo chiều).

```
src/main/java/com/twohands/admin_service/
├── application    # UseCase, @Transactional write boundary, AdminAuthorizationService usage
├── delivery       # Controller, XxxRequest/XxxResponse, @PreAuthorize / permission guard
├── domain         # Entity, rule, repository interface, AdminAuthorizationService (interface)
├── infrastructure # JPA, Redis, outbox, Auth/Commerce/Social HTTP client (khi bật)
├── config / common / exception / security
```

**Use case naming:** `SuspendUserUseCase`, `RemoveProductUseCase`, `PublishAdminEventsUseCase` — không `XxxService` generic.

**Forbidden (Admin):**
- Controller → repository trực tiếp.
- Business logic trong DTO/Controller.
- Expose JPA entity ra API.
- Publish broker trong transaction trước commit (phải outbox).
- Nhận `admin_id` từ request body — **chỉ** từ JWT (`AuthenticatedUser`).
- Mutate trực tiếp bảng Commerce/Social/Auth.
- Login credential/session trong Admin Service (delegate Auth).

## 3. Authentication & Authorization

| Mục | Quy tắc |
|-----|---------|
| Auth source | Auth Service — login/refresh/logout/revoke session |
| Admin API path | `/admin/api/v1/**` (protected: `authenticated`) |
| JWT | Cùng secret với auth-service khi test local (`JWT_ACCESS_SECRET` ≥32 chars) |
| Authorization | `FR_AuthorizeAdminApi`: validate JWT → check permission **trước** `@Transactional` use case |
| MVP claims | `JwtClaimsAdminAuthorizationService` — permissions/roles trong JWT |
| Auth HTTP | `ADMIN_AUTH_INTEGRATION_ENABLED=true` khi cần introspection/check ngoài claims |
| Fail closed | 401 missing/invalid token; 403 missing permission; không chạy domain mutation khi deny |

**Roles (ví dụ):** `MODERATOR`, `SUPPORT`, `SUPER_ADMIN`.

**Permissions (ví dụ):** `USER_SUSPEND`, `USER_RESTRICT`, `PRODUCT_REMOVE`, `REVIEW_HIDE`, `SHOP_SUSPEND`, `POST_MODERATE`, `COMMENT_MODERATE`, `SYSTEM_CONFIG_UPDATE`, `SYSTEM_ANNOUNCEMENT_PUBLISH`, `ADMIN_AUDIT_READ`, `ORDER_SUPPORT_READ`.

**Endpoint matrix (tóm tắt — chi tiết trong FR từng action):**

| Nhóm | Permission gợi ý |
|------|------------------|
| User enforcement | `USER_SUSPEND` / `USER_RESTRICT` |
| Product moderation | `PRODUCT_REMOVE` |
| Review moderation | `REVIEW_HIDE` |
| Shop moderation | `SHOP_SUSPEND` |
| Social moderation | `POST_MODERATE` / `COMMENT_MODERATE` |
| System config | `SYSTEM_CONFIG_UPDATE` |
| Announcement publish | `SYSTEM_ANNOUNCEMENT_PUBLISH` |
| Audit read | `ADMIN_AUDIT_READ` |
| Order/payment/shipment support | `ORDER_SUPPORT_READ` |

Destructive actions: bắt buộc explicit permission (không chỉ role), **reason** bắt buộc (FR enforcement/moderation).

## 4. API Contract

| Mục | Quy tắc |
|-----|---------|
| Base path | `/admin/api/v1/{resource}` |
| Production | `https://api.2hands.vn/admin/api/v1/{resource}` |
| Local | `http://localhost:3004` |
| Envelope | `docs/engineering_rules/api-standard.md` |
| Error prefix | `ADMIN-*` (`ADMIN-401`, `ADMIN-403`, `ADMIN-404`, `ADMIN-400-VALIDATION`, …) |
| DELETE | Soft delete / status transition — không hard delete mặc định |
| Health | `/actuator/health` — `permitAll` |

Khi implement controller, **ưu tiên path trong `docs/feature_requirements/admin/FR_*.md`**.

**Login/refresh/logout:** gọi Auth (`POST /auth/api/v1/...`) — Admin Service không bắt buộc endpoint gateway trừ khi FR yêu cầu proxy.

## 5. Domain State Machines (tóm tắt)

### User enforcement
```text
ACTIVE -> REVOKED
ACTIVE -> EXPIRED   (job: expires_at < now)
```
Types: `SUSPEND`, `BAN`, `RESTRICT` — mỗi transition ghi `user_enforcement_logs`.

- `SUSPEND`/`BAN`: Auth suspend + revoke sessions (event/API).
- `RESTRICT`: user login được; Social/Commerce chặn write theo policy (event).

### System announcement
```text
DRAFT -> SENT
DRAFT -> CANCELLED
SENT -> CANCELLED
```
`sent_at` set khi `SENT`. Severity: `INFO`, `WARNING`, `CRITICAL`.

### System config
- `config_key` immutable sau create.
- `value_type`: `INTEGER`, `DECIMAL`, `STRING`, `BOOLEAN`, `JSON`.
- Mọi create/update/toggle → `system_config_history` + `admin_action_logs` + outbox `SYSTEM_CONFIG_UPDATED`.

### Content moderation log
- `target_type`: `POST`, `COMMENT`, `PRODUCT`, `REVIEW`.
- `action`: `HIDE`, `REMOVE`, `RESTORE`.
- Owner service apply state; Admin chỉ log + event/API.

### Outbox
`PENDING -> PROCESSING -> PUBLISHED`; fail → `FAILED` → retry. Ghi **cùng transaction** với enforcement/moderation/config/announcement.

## 6. Audit Logging (bắt buộc)

Mọi moderation/enforcement/config destructive/critical phải ghi `admin_action_logs`:

- `admin_id`, `action_type`, `target_type`, `target_id`
- `ip_address`, `user_agent` khi có (critical)
- `request_payload` / `response_payload`: chỉ critical — **redact** token/password/secret
- `FR_LogAdminAction`, `FR_LogCriticalAdminActionPayload` — không log full token

`content_moderation_logs` cho mọi content/product/review moderation action.

## 7. Data & Schema

- Schema doc: `docs/database/admin-schema.md`
- Migration: `Services/admin-service/src/main/resources/db/migration/V1__init_admin_tables.sql`
- PK UUID; JSONB cho payload; timestamps TZ-aware.
- Không physical FK sang Auth DB.
- Indexes bắt buộc: `idx_admin_logs_admin_created`, `idx_enforcement_user`, `idx_moderation_target`, `idx_outbox_pending`.

## 8. Outbox & Kafka Topics

- Không publish trực tiếp từ use case; insert `outbox_events` trong transaction.
- `event_type`: `USER_SUSPENDED`, `PRODUCT_REMOVED`, `SYSTEM_CONFIG_UPDATED`, … (UPPER_SNAKE)
- Topic map (`AdminOutboxTopicResolver`): `admin.user.suspended`, `admin.product.removed`, `admin.config.updated`, … — thêm entry khi thêm `event_type`.
- Worker: `PublishAdminEventsUseCase`, `RetryAdminOutboxEventsUseCase` (schedulers tắt mặc định).

Catalog đầy đủ: spec §14 + `admin-schema.md` §6.

## 9. Cross-Service Integrations

| Service | Khi nào | Env |
|---------|---------|-----|
| Auth | Investigation (profile, sessions, login history, roles), enforcement sync | `ADMIN_AUTH_INTEGRATION_ENABLED`, `ADMIN_AUTH_BASE_URL` |
| Commerce | Product/review/shop moderation, order/payment/shipment support read | `ADMIN_COMMERCE_INTEGRATION_ENABLED`, `ADMIN_COMMERCE_BASE_URL` |
| Social | Post/comment moderation, restrict writes | `ADMIN_SOCIAL_INTEGRATION_ENABLED`, `ADMIN_SOCIAL_BASE_URL` |

- **Ưu tiên:** outbox event cho eventually consistent; HTTP internal API khi FR cần synchronous result.
- Consumer idempotent ở phía owner service.
- Không gọi integration trong DB transaction dài — tách read/commit local rồi publish outbox.

## 10. Background Jobs

Theo `enforcement-expiration-flow.md`, `uc-background-jobs.md`, `outbox-event-flow.md`:

- **Enforcement expiration:** `ACTIVE` + `expires_at < now` → `EXPIRED` + logs + outbox `USER_ENFORCEMENT_EXPIRED`
- **Outbox publish/retry:** `ADMIN_OUTBOX_PUBLISH_ENABLED`, `ADMIN_OUTBOX_RETRY_ENABLED`

Job bật qua config; mặc định **false** local.

## 11. Local Development

```bash
cd Infrastructure && docker compose up -d postgres-admin redis
```

Copy `Services/admin-service/.env.example` → `.env`:

- `DB_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5436/admin_db`
- `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET` / `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET` (≥32 chars, **cùng auth-service**)
- Integrations + outbox + jobs: `false` cho dev thuần CRUD/authorization

Chạy: `./gradlew bootRun` (port **3004**). Health: `/actuator/health`.

