## 13. Testing

- Unit: authorization, enforcement rules, config validation, outbox topic resolve.
- Integration: Flyway/DB, repository, API critical path (401/403 trước mutation).
- Cấu trúc: `src/test/java/.../unit/`, `.../integration/`
- Test profile: `application-test.yml`

## 14. Definition of Done (Admin Feature)

- [ ] Clean Architecture đúng layer
- [ ] API envelope + `ADMIN-*` errors
- [ ] JWT + permission trước use case write (`FR_AuthorizeAdminApi`)
- [ ] `admin_id` từ JWT; reason cho destructive action
- [ ] Audit log + moderation/enforcement logs theo FR
- [ ] Outbox event (nếu cross-service) trong cùng transaction
- [ ] Không mutate DB service khác
- [ ] Unit test logic chính; integration test khi đụng DB/API
- [ ] `docs/api_fe_behavior/admin_api_fe_behavior/<Feature>-api-and-behavior.md`

## 15. MVP Out of Scope

Refund/dispute thực thi, payout reversal, admin case management, ML moderation, admin credential DB riêng, notification dismissal tracking trong Admin DB.

